metadata.name: V 2022
metadata.description:
This token is a verifiable ticket for admission to V at Scope Beach on December 1, 2022, in Miami, Florida. This ticket will harness the power of Web3 token-gating to grant you access to a celebration of art, culture, live musical performances, and more.

To be admitted to V at Scope Beach, attendees must hold this token and register it via tokenproof's mobile app. You will need to show proof of ownership via tokenproof at the door. 

Terms and Conditions Apply, US Only, For Ages 21+ - [https://vayner3.com/v-terms-conditions/](https://vayner3.com/v-terms-conditions/)
